<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-10-15T17:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-07-28T18:00:00-05:00" n="262" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d262">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.U.16.</note>
                        <head><hi rend="smallcaps">Article 52</hi></head>
                        <dateline>
                            <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00">undated</date>
                        </dateline>
                        <list>
                            <label>1.</label>
                            <item>Paragraph 1: The words, “30,000 Carabinieri” should be substituted
                                for “65,000 Carabinieri”, and “215,000” for “250,000”.</item>
                            <label>2.</label>
                            <item>The following new paragraph should be inserted after paragraph 1:
                                    <quote rend="blockquote">
                                    <p>“2. In no case shall any officer or non-commissioned officer
                                        of the former Fascist Militia or of the former Fascist
                                        Republican Army be admitted with Officer’s or
                                        non-commissioned officer’s rank to the Italian Army, Navy or
                                        Air Force.”</p>
                                </quote></item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>